Crawl into the dark and unsettlingly spooky, doll-filled bar at The Butterfly Club and get ready to party &quot;like grisly ghouls from every tomb are closing in to seal your doom&quot; (also from Thriller rap). Experience bone-chillingly beautiful halloween-themed cocktails. Save your hell-damned soul buy grabbing tickets to one of our sinfully good shows. Slink into our secret downstairs bar for a witching-hour cabaret with special surprise performers coming out of every cobwebbed nook. Best costume receives an evil prize MMWAAAHAHAHAHAHAA...

